notesStmt.note: Folio 154r: the names of the signs of zodiac and seven planets in Hebrew and Latin.
Folio 155v-156r: a list of books in a late Italian cursive script.
Manuscript description based on Margoliouth, G.: Catalogue of the Hebrew and Samaritan Manuscripts in the British Museum, London 1965.
